		<h3>Terms of Service</h3>
		<p>The following are the CliqBit™ Terms of Service (“Terms”) for the use of any CliqBit™ applications. Please read the Terms carefully. By downloading, accessing, or using the applications, websites, or other products or services of CliqBit™, LLC (“CliqBit™”, “we” or “us”), or the services, features, or functionality jointly offered with other companies through our application or website (collectively, the “Services”), you agree to be bound by these Terms.</p>
		<p>These Terms affect your legal rights and obligations, if you do not agree to these Terms of Service, do not use any CliqBit™ Applications or Services. In the event you use a service, feature, or functionality that is operated by a third party and made available through our Services (including Services we jointly offer with the third party), each party’s terms will govern as to the respective party’s relationship with you. In these instances, we will take steps to make the third party’s terms available to you before you begin to use the service, feature, or functionality.</p>
		<p>CliqBit™ is not a money-services business. It does not transmit any funds. To the extent such functionality is made available in the Services, it is provided by an unaffiliated third party, and like any other third-party service, subject to their terms of use.</p>
		<p>Arbitration Notice: Except for certain types of disputes described in the arbitration clause below, you agree that disputes between you and CliqBit™, LLC will be resolved by mandatory, binding arbitration and by using the Services, you waive any right to enter into a class-action lawsuit or class-wide arbitration.</p>
		<br>
		<h3>Have a sense of humor</h3>
		<p>Our Terms of Service form a proper legal contract. The majority of the Services have been developed to allow our users to share humor and to observe and even participate with the humor of others. Everyone has his or her own sense of humor. So, please be aware of others’ sensitivity and enjoy this application in the positive manner in which it has been developed. Our Terms of Service allow us to continue to improve our applications, while at the same time ensuring that a few inappropriate users don’t ruin everyone else’s experience with the Services. Use your common sense: Keep posting your humorous “Bits” to your “Cliqs”, and please do not post items that others won’t want to see.</p>
		<br>
