		<p>CliqBit™ is for the use of people who are at least 13 years old. Persons under the age of 13 are prohibited from creating CliqBit™ accounts. Some Services may be subject to separate terms from CliqBit™ or third parties that contain further age requirements. If you are under 18 and use those Services, you may be violating the third party’s governing terms, which we deem a violation of these Terms, as well.</p>
		<p>Before using the Services, you must affirm that you are either at least 13 years of age and are fully able and competent to enter into the terms, conditions, obligations, affirmations, representations, and warranties set forth in these Terms, and to abide by and comply with these Terms. In addition, you will be asked to affirm that you have not been previously suspended or removed from the Services and do not have more than one CliqBit™ account.</p>
		<p>CliqBit™ may, at its sole discretion, refuse to offer or allow Services to any person or entity. We may, without notice and at CliqBit’s sole discretion, terminate your right to use the Services, or any portion thereof, and may also block or prevent your future access to and use of the Services or any portion thereof.</p>
