		<p>The Services consist of interactive features and areas of the CliqBit™ applications that allow users to create, post, transmit, and/or store content, including but not limited to posts, photos, videos, text, graphics, links, or other materials (collectively, “User Content”). You are responsible for all third party data charges that you incur when using the Services. Keep in mind that your User Content may be viewable by others and that you have the ability to control who can access your user content by designating what CliqBit™ feed your information is on and for how long. Users who post to their “Cliqs” should be aware that the group manager, known as a “Cliq’r”, may add new people to the Cliq at their discretion. It is your responsibility to stay updated on the membership changes that inherently occur within each Cliq. You have the option to leave a Cliq if you are dissatisfied with member(s) in the Cliq for any reason.</p>
		<p>It’s important to be aware that any information shared online may be accessed by others. CliqBit™, LLC is not responsible for the actions of those who obtain the content that you have chosen to share. You are solely responsible for your User Content and any claims arising therefrom, and CliqBit™ is not responsible or liable for misuse of any User Content or any claims arising therefrom.</p>
